    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/6843ff48522f2e9d6449367cb2ee0a0a.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/6843ff48522f2e9d6449367cb2ee0a0a.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/6843ff48522f2e9d6449367cb2ee0a0a.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>我们：革命是一款拥有独特艺术风格的游戏，背景设定在法国大革命那段血腥与疑虑重重的时代，在那个年代，朋友与敌人往往难以分辨。作为革命法庭的法官，你将在这个世界中艰难前行，做出判决，参与危险的政治游戏，并尽一切努力避免被作为革命的敌人送上断头台。一天结束时，你还需要面对家庭对你决定的看法，而他们的想法往往与你不同。 </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/fb837f3bb9dd780f9680ddb701d8aa20.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/fb837f3bb9dd780f9680ddb701d8aa20.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/fb837f3bb9dd780f9680ddb701d8aa20.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong> </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><strong><i>我们：革命[\\i][/b]的剧情将让你身处于道德模糊的境地，没有明确的正解，你的每一个决定都充满灰色地带。生杀大权是一种沉重的负担，也是一种责任与力量，它将影响整个革命的命运。每次做出判决、分配任务、发表演讲和编织幕后政治阴谋时，请牢记这一点。本作专为喜欢面对道德抉择、做出复杂个人选择，并沉浸于精妙政治阴谋世界的玩家打造。</i></strong></i></strong><br><strong><i><strong><i> </i></strong></i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><i><strong><strong><strong>在《我们：革命》中你将体验。</strong></strong></strong></i></i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>决定谁生谁死，亲手书写历史。</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/3c71f7939491d67a3462976b50696a92.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=590 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/3c71f7939491d67a3462976b50696a92.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/3c71f7939491d67a3462976b50696a92.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><i> </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>体验如同大仲马与约瑟夫·康拉德笔下法国大革命的压抑氛围。</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/202974c6c2904ee022ab77bfb97a30d0.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=590 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/202974c6c2904ee022ab77bfb97a30d0.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/202974c6c2904ee022ab77bfb97a30d0.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>主持数十起独特而充满道德挑战的审判案件。</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/44d9ec1444e4c427c388ca521bfcb48f.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=590 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/44d9ec1444e4c427c388ca521bfcb48f.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/44d9ec1444e4c427c388ca521bfcb48f.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>面对家庭对你裁决的质疑——他们或许并不认同你的选择。 </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/7a8cf7772964b40a30e0dc41666f06fa.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=590 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/7a8cf7772964b40a30e0dc41666f06fa.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/7a8cf7772964b40a30e0dc41666f06fa.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><i><i><i><i><i><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong> </strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></i></i></i></i></i></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>掌控法庭——审问证人、分析线索、阅读报告并做出判决。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/e896a477892e191b1f626b9425d37278.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=590 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/e896a477892e191b1f626b9425d37278.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/e896a477892e191b1f626b9425d37278.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>与争权夺利的各派系打交道——拉拢盟友或让对手从此消失！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/b35e4263b52d6b09a9b7407488ea4cb3.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=590 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/b35e4263b52d6b09a9b7407488ea4cb3.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/b35e4263b52d6b09a9b7407488ea4cb3.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>融合多种类型玩法，结合案件构建、阴谋策划与回合制战术。</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/33998aa6cf98f85f646b5565cb9cdae2.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=590 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/33998aa6cf98f85f646b5565cb9cdae2.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/33998aa6cf98f85f646b5565cb9cdae2.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>欣赏将简洁多边形与革命时代新古典艺术融合的独特视觉风格。 </i></strong><br><strong><i> </i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/5a106dd367f0b0d345cbef40129f7b39.poster.avif?t=1770487124\" width=590 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/5a106dd367f0b0d345cbef40129f7b39.webm?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/736850/extras/5a106dd367f0b0d345cbef40129f7b39.mp4?t=1770487124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><i> </i></strong><br><strong><i> </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>我们：革命是一段象征性的故事，松散地基于法国大革命时期的真实事件。体验动荡年代中的人生!</i></strong></p></li></ul>",
